languages.text: "Не провалился. Выбор был сделан. Просто новый Висирь Кровавой паутины будет более инаков, чем думалось мне. Нити переплетутся сильнее, узор изменится, но... Служение Ему продолжится".

"It has not failed. The choice has been made. Certainly, the new Vizsier of the Bloodspun Web will bring more change than I imagined. The threads will be more intertwined. The pattern will be different. But... the service to Him will continue."

languages.text: 「失敗ではありません。決定は下された。やはりブラッドスパン・ウェブの新しいヴィジールは、想像以上の変化をもたらしてくれそうです。糸はさらに複雑に絡み合うでしょう。模様も変化するでしょう。けれども…あの方への奉仕は続くのです」

languages.text: “计划并没有失败，她已经做出了选择。诚然，新任宿老会带来的变化，恐怕比我想象的要多得多。所有丝线都会以更加复杂的方式交织在一起，勾勒出不同的图案，不过……织血罗网依然会侍奉不死之神，这一点没有变。”
languages.original_text: "It has not failed. The choice has been made. Certainly, the new Vizsier of the Bloodspun Web will bring more change than I imagined. The threads will be more intertwined. The pattern will be different. But... the service to Him will continue."

languages.text: "Er ist nicht gescheitert. Die Wahl ist getroffen. Gewiss wird der neue Wesir des Blutgesponnenen Netzes mehr Veränderungen bringen, als ich es mir vorgestellt habe. Die Fäden werden stärker verflochten sein. Das Muster wird anders sein. Doch ... der Dienst an ihm wird weitergehen."

languages.text: "Başarısız olmadı. Seçim yapıldı. Muhakkak ki Kanipi Ağı'nın yeni Vezir'i, tasavvur ettiğimden çok daha fazla değişim getirecek. İplikler, daha da çok iç içe geçecek. Motifler farklı olacak. Fakat... O'na olan hizmetimiz devam edecek."
languages.original_text: "It has not failed. The choice has been made. Certainly, the new Vizsier of the Bloodspun Web will bring more change than I imagined. The threads will be more intertwined. The pattern will be different. But... the service to Him will continue."
